          "INC-SOURCE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "incident_source": [
                  "D-T"
                ],
                "reaction": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Neutrons were produced by the T(D,n)a reaction",
                "with a D beam current of about 500 uA. The thickness",
                "of the solid tritium-titanium (T-Ti) target used in",
                "the generator was 1.0 mg/cm2 and the energy of",
                "incident D beam was 300 keV. The incident neutron",
                "energy was determined to be (14.60+-0.40) MeV, with a",
                "neutron yield of about (2-5)x10**10 n/s.",
                "The relative neutron fluence was monitored by the",
                "accompanying alpha particles."
              ]
            }
